Aim_headshot2 - Fun / Aim
Aimmap for CSS by uF2k The Ripper
Visit www.uF2k.com

This map was designed for 5v5 matches,
but will support up to 40 players.

Counter-Terrorists: Kill the Terrorist.
Terrorists: Kill the Counter-Terrorists team.

German:

Möglichkeiten zu sterben oder sterben zu
lassen.
